@M_KOJO_ENCOUNTER_K128
;初対面、挨拶のタイミング
;TALENTの変更はここでどうぞ。
;経験の変更は齟齬が出る場合がありますので、CSVを修正し同梱する事を推奨します
;note - this intro relies that you meet Urumi at her usual spot (at the river), probably need more instances to catch most of possible spots
PRINTFORMW 「Hello friend, I believe this is the first time we met.」
;met - typo, tweak
PRINTFORMDW You turn your head to meet the gaze of a bovine woman who is smiling back at you.
;voluminous - typo
PRINTFORMDL You see that her voluminous hair is mismatched, with one side being black and the one almost ghostly white.
PRINTFORMDW Two red horns emerging from her scalp.
PRINTFORMW 「I'm Urumi Ushizaki. I'm just a humble fisherwoman that lives at Children's Limbo. And who you might be?」
PRINTFORMDL
;player choice
CALL NAME_SET_K128

;note - important distinction - MASTERNAME:(chara num) - is a custom way the character refers to PC, CALLNAME:MASTER - is PC's default name, first is useful in spoken lines, second is used in descriptions (for example)
PRINTFORMW 「%MASTERNAME:128%, is it?」
;tweak, note: PRINT_DIALOGUE is explained later
CALL PRINT_DIALOGUE, @"Let me give you some friendly advice: don't try to cross the Sanzu River on your own, that's a mistake many outsiders make only to meet their doom.", "w"

;If Urumi is [Tall]
IF TALENT:体型 > 0
	PRINTFORMDW You can't help but stare at her breasts, with them being about eye level with you.
	PRINTFORMDW You turn your head looking at nowhere, trying not to be impolite.  
	PRINTFORMDW You hear a small chuckle coming from the bovine woman.
ENDIF
PRINTFORML
;tweak
PRINTFORMDW Urumi seems to have been carrying something the whole time, but now that she's closer, you can get a better look at it.
;tweak
PRINTFORMDW It's a stone carved in the shape of a bovine baby.
PRINTFORMW 「Are you curious about this little one? Would you like to try holding it?」
PRINTFORMDW Without waiting for your answer, she shoves the stone in your arms, readjusting the cow patterned jacket on her shoulders.
PRINTFORMDW You gently hold the stone baby close to you, just like a real one.
PRINTFORML
PRINTFORMDW Urumi rests her hands on her hips watching you intently.
PRINTFORMW 「That's a good look on you. You'd make a good parent someday.」
;tweak
PRINTFORMDW But before you can answer, a sudden pressure on your arms grabs your attention.
;tweak
PRINTFORMDW The stone baby you're holding seems to be getting heavier by the second. Its bovine features remain unchanged.
PRINTFORML

;IF Fighting skill F to D (note - practical skills start from E rank (0 to 6))
IF ABL:MASTER:戦闘能力 <= 1
	PRINTFORMDW The baby sudden weight gain causes you drop the small statue on the floor with a loud *thud* opening a small crater into the ground.
	PRINTFORMW 「Oh? Did something happen?」
	PRINTFORMDW Urumi walks up to you.
	PRINTFORMW 「Sorry about that, I should've warned you that this baby is heavier than it looks.」
	PRINTFORMDW She smiles and picks the baby up the from the floor.
	PRINTFORMW 「Oh, don't feel bad. This little one is sturdier than it looks. I'm sure one day you will be strong enough to hold it.」
;IF Fighting Skill C to A
ELSEIF ABL:MASTER:戦闘能力 <= 4
	PRINTFORMDW You tension your legs and hug the stone baby even closer to you. Its sudden heaviness showing no sign of ceasing.
	PRINTFORMDW Beads of sweat begin to form on your forehead but thankfully before the weight becomes too much to bear, Urumi reaches for you.
	PRINTFORMW 「Is something wrong, %MASTERNAME:128%? You look like a mess.」
	PRINTFORMDW She scoops the baby from you. 
	PRINTFORMW 「Sorry about that. If you're wondering, yes, that is my doing. I simply can't resist the urge to pull this prank when I meet someone new.」
	PRINTFORMDW Urumi chuckles wholeheartedly.
	PRINTFORMW 「I've got a good feeling about you and I'm happy that you held your ground, however I'm sure you can do better if you put more heart into it.」
	PRINTFORML
	PRINTFORMDW You wipe the sweat from your brow and stare at the woman in front of you.
	PRINTFORMDW Her smile seems a bit more genuine and relaxed than before, as if she seems satisfied with what she sees.
	;+200 Favorability bonus.
	CALL CHANGE_CFLAG(2, 128, 200)
;IF Fighting Skill S-EX;
ELSE
	PRINTFORMDW You look down at the stone baby with an unfazed look on your face.
	;tweak
	PRINTFORMDW A normal person would struggle under the sudden pressure of the object they're carrying gaining weight at such a rapid rate.
	;note - look deep where???
	PRINTFORMDW Thanks to your rigorous training, you hold the small statue without trouble. You lift your head and look deep 
	PRINTFORML
	PRINTFORMDW Her eyebrows arc inward, but her lazy smile remains unchanged.
	PRINTFORMDW You can almost feel yourself drilling a few inches into the floor.
	PRINTFORMDW Upon seeing your unfazed stance, Urumi briefly looks shocked, only to smile warmly at you.
	PRINTFORML
	PRINTFORMDW She stands there for a few seconds, her tail swishing from side to side.
	PRINTFORMW 「Impressive... Ah!」
	;tweak
	PRINTFORMDW When she realizes that you might have heard her, her body stiffens for a moment.
	PRINTFORMDW There is a deep blush on her face that wasn't there a few moments ago.
	PRINTFORMDW Saying nothing, she scoops the baby from you with her free arm.
	PRINTFORMW 「Sorry about that. If you're wondering, yes, that is my doing. I simply can't resist the urge to pull this prank on everybody I first meet.」
	PRINTFORMW 「But I must say that you're the first one that managed to hold it without any trouble, you've... piqued my interest, friend.」
	PRINTFORMDW Urumi moves a stray strand of hair behind one ear while giving you a warm smile.
	PRINTFORMW 「I think you deserve a reward for that, don't you think?」
	;tweak
	PRINTFORMDW Urumi gives you one of her freshly caught, high quality fish.
	PRINTFORMW 「I need to get those home before they spoil. I'll be back in a moment if you want to talk or... something else.」
	PRINTFORMDW Urumi turns and heads to her shack with a different sway on her hips. It's quite clear you gave her quite the first impression.
	;500+ Favorability + 1 Rare fish.
	CALL CHANGE_CFLAG(2, 128, 500)
