	PRINTFORMW 「I know it is weird to ask, but can you hold on to this little one again?」
	PRINTFORMDW She carefully passes the stone baby to you.
	PRINTFORMDW You firmly hold the rock carving, getting ready in case it begins increasing its weight again.
	PRINTFORMDW Surprisingly, though, it still remains fairly light, making you look down and wonder why it isn't weighing as much as before.
	PRINTFORMDW You feel Urumi's hands clapping on your shoulders as she moves her head close to yours, you raise your head in reflex.

