@M_KOJO_SPEVENT_K128_2(ARG,ARG:1)
;口上主はTARGET
;地の文表示
;--------------------------------------------------
;記入チェック（=0, 非表示、1, 表示）
LOCAL = 1
;-------------
IF LOCAL
	;-------------------------------------------------
	;小分岐
	;-------------------------------------------------
	;Confession
	;After this dialogue is displayed, the player will have a choice to become the character's lover or turn them down.
	;告白内容
	;この告白内容表示後に受けるかどうかの選択分が表示されます
	;記入チェック（=0, 非表示、1, 表示）
	LOCAL:1 = 1
	;-------------------------------------------------
	IF LOCAL:1 && ARG == 0
		;TO BE REDONE
		;repeat
		IF CEVENT("RepeatConfession")
			PRINTFORMW 「I don't know how you do it, %MASTERNAME:128%...」
			PRINTFORMDW Urumi says with a warm smile.
			PRINTFORMW 「But thanks to you, I had another fantastic day.」
			PRINTFORMDW Urumi looks deep into your eyes, before closing them.
			PRINTFORMW 「How come someone like you hasn't already been taken? Ah!」
			PRINTFORMDW Upon hearing what she just said, her eyes open wide in shock.
			PRINTFORMW 「Sorry! It's just that... No...」
			PRINTFORMDW She turns her face in shame but quickly recover, looking deep into your eyes.
			PRINTFORMW 「I still very much like you %MASTERNAME:128%.」
			PRINTFORMDW Urumi reaches and grasps one of your arms.
			PRINTFORMW 「If the other girls are too stupid to not value someone like you, they can only blame themselves for their loss.」
			PRINTFORMW 「I still love you %MASTERNAME:128%... Have your feelings about me changed?」
			;-----------
		ELSE
			;note - breakeng is used for very long descriptive lines (>145 characters)
			PRINTFORMDW %BREAKENG(@"Urumi walks side by side with you. She gently hugs one of your arms but you begin having trouble keeping a steady pace as she begins slowing down, finally coming to a halt.")%
			PRINTFORMW 「%MASTERNAME:128%... I must confess something to you.」
			PRINTFORMDW Urumi says with an unusually serious tone.
			PRINTFORMW 「The days we spent together have been some of my happiest but...」
			PRINTFORMDW She gently places a hand on your chest before continuing.
			PRINTFORMW 「I was content enough with how simple my life was. Waking up early, fishing, and see my days pass by peacefully.」
			PRINTFORMDW She look downward for a moment, before returning her gaze up.
			PRINTFORMW 「For the first time, I yearn for more %MASTERNAME:128%. All because of you.」
			;note - PRINT_DIALOGUE is same as breakeng, but for spoken lines
			CALL PRINT_DIALOGUE, @"I've helped a lot of people who have accidentally found their way to the river, and it made me happy to see them go back to where they came from.", "w"
			PRINTFORMW 「I know it's selfish of me to ask, but I do want you to stay here, %MASTERNAME:128%. You've won this lonely woman's heart.」
			PRINTFORMW 「I love you %MASTERNAME:128%. Will you accept my feelings?」
			;set up the character flag for cevent function, it uses CALLF instruction because of how it's implemented unlike other functions
			CALLF SET_CEVENT("RepeatConfession")
		ENDIF
		RETURN 1
	ENDIF
	;-------------------------------------------------
	;Confession accepted (player and character become lovers)
	;告白オッケー（恋人が付く）
	;記入チェック（=0, 非表示、1, 表示）
	LOCAL:1 = 1
	;-------------------------------------------------
	IF LOCAL:1 && ARG == 1
		PRINTFORMW 「%MASTERNAME:128%. %MASTERNAME:128%!」
		;amrs - typo
		PRINTFORMDW Urumi walks up and wraps her arms around you.
		;agaisnt - typo
		PRINTFORMDW You can't help but feel her hefty breasts pressing against you.
		PRINTFORMDW You two stand like that for a few moments. You can hear her breath being erratic.
		PRINTFORMDW As if she holding back tears.
		PRINTFORMW 「I know I'm an indolent woman that lives quietly by the river.」
		PRINTFORMW 「And there are also younger, cuter girls than me, but...」
		PRINTFORMDW Urumi ends the hug, but not before landing a peck on your lips.
		PRINTFORMW 「I promise you won't regret this... I'll love you with all my heart.」
		PRINTFORMDW Urumi grabs one of your hands and place it on her cheek.
		;note - if the spoken sentence ends with tilde, you can skip the punctuation at the end
		PRINTFORMW 「Darling♪～」
		RETURN 1
	ENDIF
	;-------------------------------------------------
	;Confession rejected
	;告白失敗
	;記入チェック（=0, 非表示、1, 表示）
	LOCAL:1 = 1
	;-------------------------------------------------
	IF LOCAL:1 && ARG == 2
		PRINTFORMW 「...It's alright.」
		PRINTFORMDW Urumi closes her eyes and put on a strong smile.
		PRINTFORMDW Is she alright?
		PRINTFORMW 「There's no need to feel guilty.」
		;open - typo
		PRINTFORMDW She opens her eyes again.
		PRINTFORMW 「I won't let something like this ruin what we have now.」
		;note - when describing character thoughts with parenthesis, use double-width ones, replacing the dialogue brackets
		PRINTFORMW （But I won't give up, I won't lose you to anyone.）
		PRINTFORMDW Urumi attempts to act nonchalant, but you can see her hugging the stone baby tighter.
		PRINTFORMW 「Ah, I think we should be going. It's getting pretty late.」
		PRINTFORMDW She begins walking ahead of you.
		PRINTFORMW （...One day, maybe...）
		RETURN 1
	ENDIF
ENDIF
RETURN 1

